{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "lentera-karir-collection",
    "name": "LenteraKarir API",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": "Postman collection for LenteraKarir backend API.\n\n## 🚀 PANDUAN CEPAT PENGGUNAAN\n\n### Step 1: Import Collection\n1. Buka Postman\n2. Klik tombol Import (atau Ctrl+O)\n3. Pilih file Postman-Collection-LenteraKarir.json\n4. Klik Import\n\n### Step 2: Setup Variables\n1. Di sidebar kiri, klik collection \"LenteraKarir API\"\n2. Klik tab \"Variables\"\n3. Isi nilai untuk:\n   - baseUrl: http://localhost:3000\n   - adminToken: (paste JWT token admin dari Supabase)\n   - userToken: (paste JWT token user dari Supabase)\n4. Klik Save\n\n### Step 3: Testing Endpoint\n1. Buka endpoint dari list (misal: Auth → Sync User)\n2. Klik tombol \"Send\"\n3. Lihat response di panel bawah\n\n### Step 4: Workflow Testing\nUkuran optimal untuk testing:\n1. Public Catalog → List Learning Paths (public, no auth)\n2. Admin: Learning Paths → Create (perlu adminToken)\n3. Admin: Courses & Modules → Create Course (perlu adminToken)\n4. Admin: Quiz Engine → Create Quiz (perlu adminToken)\n5. Payments → Create Checkout (perlu userToken)\n6. Learning (User) → Get Dashboard (perlu userToken)\n\n### Cara Dapatkan Token Supabase:\n- Via Frontend: Login → buka DevTools (F12) → Application → cari supabase-auth-token\n- Via Supabase Dashboard: Buka Authentication → Users → copy User ID\n- Via Curl: POST ke https://YOUR-SUPABASE-URL/auth/v1/token?grant_type=password\n\n### Tips:\n- Setiap response yang berisi ID, copy value tersebut ke collection variable yang sesuai (misal: response id \"LP-123\" → set lpId ke LP-123)\n- Gunakan Pre-request Scripts untuk otomasi (lihat tab Tests di setiap request)\n- Untuk mendapat bantuan, baca error message di response panel dengan teliti\n\n### Troubleshooting:\n- 404 Not Found? Pastikan server jalan (npm run dev) dan baseUrl benar\n- 401 Unauthorized? Periksa adminToken atau userToken sudah diisi dengan benar\n- Variable tidak terisi? Gunakan format {{namaVariable}} (double curly braces)\n\nDokumentasi lengkap: Lihat file POSTMAN_GUIDE.md di folder backend."
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "adminToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "userToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "lpId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "courseId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "moduleId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "quizId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "questionId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "optionId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "attemptId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "userId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "refreshToken", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Sync User (Supabase -> MySQL)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/sync",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"user_id\": \"auth0|123\",\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/refresh-token",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refresh_token\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Public Catalog",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Learning Paths",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/catalog/learning-paths"
          }
